  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbe \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc6\u0ba9: \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bb2 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b95\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Resignation of President: Red Sea Declaration",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "All religious leaders including Mahanayake Theras and civil representatives signed the Red Sea Declaration in Kandy yesterday to create better governance in the country.",
        "It mainly states that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa should resign from the post of Executive President unconditionally as he addressed the nation on May 11, 2022.",
        "Similarly, it is stated in the declaration that only one leader recognized by the Sri Lankan people and the international community should be appointed to the post of President.",
        "Also, it is mentioned in the Red Sea Declaration that an all-party government should be appointed for a certain period of time and the 22nd amendment should be brought and passed as soon as possible beyond the 19th amendment.",
        "It further indicated that the President of an all-party government would hold office until a general election or a presidential election was held and the term should be specified."
      ],
